#Cstrike Website from the 2000

This is a basic rebuild of the 2000 website of Counter Strike!
It has a Flask backend so there its possible to add some automatic downloadlink add in later.
Its still a pretty basic site so it should run on old low ram pcs.

##Modernisation

I modernised some stuff mainly the Html, it being 26 years old dint quite work that well.
This also counts to all links they are ether fixed for Flask or dead.
The banner Ads can be freely customiced in the AdBanner.js file!!

##Template

This recriation is manly a template so other people can get inspiered or use it as a base.
So pretty much all content is stripped out of the Website other then some example stuff to show where stuff should go.

I will personly base my main website on this which will also be realesed. 

###Filestructure

There is a Frontend folder which just contains half fixed Html files (More or less the original files).
Then there is the Flask Folder this one contains the fully rewritten website.
Lastly there will be a Home folder which will include my personal site.

The .venv is not included but a requierments.txt.


